《'''把愛傳出去－援助日本震災專輯'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Songs for Japan'''''}}）是為[[2011年日本東北地方太平洋近海地震|2011年日本東北地方太平洋近海地震]]賑災而合作發行的[[公益歌曲|慈善]][[合輯|合輯]]，由[[音樂產業|世界四大音樂唱片公司]]—[[EMI|EMI]]、[[索尼音樂娛樂|索尼音樂娛樂]]、[[環球唱片|環球唱片]]和[[華納音樂集團|華納音樂集團]]聯合推出。2011年3月25日由環球唱片負責發行，在[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]上提供下載服務。<ref>{{Cite press release|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-music-effort-launches-songs-for-japan-album-on-itunes-to-benefit-japan-disaster-relief-118658009.html|title=Global Music Effort Launches "Songs for Japan" Album on iTunes to Benefit Japan Disaster Relief|date=2011-03-25|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|access-date=2011-04-03|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207105022/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-music-effort-launches-songs-for-japan-album-on-itunes-to-benefit-japan-disaster-relief-118658009.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MTV">{{cite web|title=Songs For Japan Includes Eminem, Justin Bieber, Lady Gaga And More|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1660688/songs-japan-includes-eminem-justin-bieber-lady-gaga-more.jhtml|first=James|last=Montgomery|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=2011-03-25|accessdate=2011-04-03|archive-date=2011-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429010601/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1660688/songs-japan-includes-eminem-justin-bieber-lady-gaga-more.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>專輯中收錄的曲目的版權所有者均同意所有收益都捐獻給[[日本紅十字會|日本紅十字會]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=John Lennon, Justin Bieber, Lady Gaga, Katy Perry, Josh Groban hits together on 'Songs for Japan' benefit album|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/03/john-lennon-justin-bieber-lady-gaga-katy-perry-josh-groban-hits-songs-for-japan-benefit.html|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=2011-03-25|access-date=2011-04-03|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209060920/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/03/john-lennon-justin-bieber-lady-gaga-katy-perry-josh-groban-hits-songs-for-japan-benefit.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Major Labels Join for Compilation for Japan|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=13222633|publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|agency=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|date=2011-03-25}}</ref>2011年4月4日由索尼音樂娛樂發行實體唱片。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idCATRE72O4U020110325?sp=true|title=Major record labels join for Japan relief album|date=March 25, 2011|first=Mike|last=Collett-White|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|location=London|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2011-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111125175203/http://ca.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idCATRE72O4U020110325?sp=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==評價==
雖然專輯賑災的善舉得到很多人的讚揚，但除了[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]的重編曲版《[[Born_This_Way_(歌曲)|Born This Way]]》之外，其它歌曲都是已經發行過的，和[[2010年海地地震|海地大地震]]時歐美群星為賑災而發行的專輯《[[Hope_for_Haiti_Now|Hope for Haiti Now]]》不同，引起部分人士的批評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2011/03/songs-for-japan-justin-bieber-bob-dylan-and-beyonce-unite-for-random-compilation-of-unoriginal-music/73049/#|title='Songs for Japan': Justin Bieber, Bob Dylan, and Beyonce Unite for Random Compilation of Unoriginal Music
|publisher=[[亞特蘭大報|亞特蘭大報]]|first=Kevin|last=Fallon|date=2011-03-25}}</ref>

